{Thrash}

    Thrash growled as he lay on the ground, his systems had taken a shot but
his injuries at best were managable. He had hoped that one or two of the
fools battling him had flew down to inspect his prone form but with the
sound of weapons fire in the air the bot rolled quickly to one side then the
other accepting a minor blast along a shoulder.

    Trying to stand he found his legs entangled in a net of some kind and
growled even more watching two others fighting off the maximal scum, opening
a comm channel he spoke, &quot;Thanks for the reprieve.&quot;

    Sitting up as best he could he reached down snapping a sharp tooth from
the shark maw at his chest and began sawing through the bonds that
restricted his legs....
